sourcesContent:
//Order of appearance//

let container = {
  backgroundColor: "#022129",
  border: "2px solid #063b50",
  height: "98.4%", 
  margin: "10px 0 0 10px",
  width: "28.8%"
}

let mainTitleContainer = {
  backgroundColor: "#063b50",
  color: "white",
  display: "flex",
  flexDirection: "row",
  fontSize: "17px",
  height: "25px",
  paddingTop: "3px",
  textAlign: "center",
  width: "100%"
}

let hcsImage = {
  cursor: "pointer", 
  float: "left", 
  height: "80%", 
  margin: "auto 0 auto 10px"
}

let mainTitle = {
  lineHeight: "20px",
  width: "100%"
}

let closeContainer = {
  display: "flex", 
  width: "100%"
}

let close = {
  cursor: "pointer", 
  fontSize: "25px", 
  lineHeight: "25px", 
  marginRight: "6px",
  marginLeft: "auto",
  transform: "rotate(45deg)", 
  userSelect: "none", 
  width: "auto"
}

let profileContainer = {
  border: "2px solid #044b5f", 
  height: "71%",
  margin: "6px auto 0px auto", 
  width: "97%"
}

let subTitle = {
  backgroundColor: "#044b5f",
  color: "white",
  textAlign: "center"
}

let profileContentContainer = {
  backgroundColor: "#e4f7ff",
  fontSize: "11px",
  height: "96%", 
  paddingBottom: "3px",
  width: "100%"
}

let profileContentSeparator = {
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  display: "flex", 
  height: "1px",
  margin: "8px 5px 0 5px",
  width: "100%"
}

let historyContainer = {
  backgroundColor: "#e4f7ff", 
  border: "2px solid #044b5f",
  height: "22.5%",
  margin: "7px auto 0px auto",
  width: "97%"
}

let historyContentContainer = {
  height: "165px"
}

export {
  container,
  mainTitleContainer,
  hcsImage,
  mainTitle,
  closeContainer,
  close,
  profileContainer,
  subTitle,
  profileContentContainer,
  profileContentSeparator,
  historyContainer,
  historyContentContainer  
}
